videos.description: Purdue guard Carsen Edwards picks up the rebound and runs to the other end, passing through Illinois' defense and scoring an easy layup in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Edwards goes coast to coast uncontested) 2017/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edwards goes coast to coast uncontested

videos.description: Purdue forward Vince Edwards posts up against a defender and switches his pivot foot on a spin move, which results in a no-call for travelling and the referees getting an earful from Illinois coach John Groce.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Refs miss a blatant travel call on Purdue) 2017/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Refs miss a blatant travel call on Purdue

videos.description: Purdue center Isaac Haas makes an unbelievable block on Illinois guard Te'Jon Lucas with help from the backboard in a 91-68 win over the Fighting Illini.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Purdue's big man makes a LeBron-like block) 2017/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue's big man makes a LeBron-like block
